's clear that Microsoft's car efforts have progressed over the past year, but the company still isn't ready to launch its own Windows 10 integration. |access-date=2019-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213030923/https://www.theverge.com/2015/9/16/9336205/microsoft-windows-in-the-car-cortana-concept |archive-date=2019-02-13 }}</ref>。

