=== 主要 ===
小娜可以设置提醒，无需键盘输入就能识别语音，并且可以使用[[Bing|必应搜索引擎]]提供的信息来回答问题<ref>{{Cite web |title=My interests and Cortana |url=http://www.windowsphone.com/en-us/how-to/wp8/apps/my-interests-and-cortana |accessdate=2014-06-19 |author=Microsoft |publisher=Windows Phone |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707015844/http://www.windowsphone.com/en-us/how-to/wp8/apps/my-interests-and-cortana |archivedate=2014-07-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Remind me, Cortana |url=http://www.windowsphone.com/en-us/how-to/wp8/apps/remind-me-cortana |accessdate=2014-06-19 |author=Microsoft |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707011106/http://www.windowsphone.com/en-us/how-to/wp8/apps/remind-me-cortana |archivedate=2014-07-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=The story of Cortana, Microsoft's Siri killer |url=https://www.theverge.com/2014/4/2/5570866/cortana-windows-phone-8-1-digital-assistant |accessdate=2014-06-19 |author=Warren |date=2014-04-02 |first=Tom |publisher=The Verge |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151204151415/http://www.theverge.com/2014/4/2/5570866/cortana-windows-phone-8-1-digital-assistant |archive-date=2015-12-04 }}</ref>。

小娜通过“记事本”（{{Lang-en|Notebook}}）功能存储个人信息，如兴趣、位置数据、提醒和联系人。它可以利用并添加这些数据来学习用户的特定模式和行为。用户可以查看和设定收集哪些信息，以便对自己的隐私进行控制。<ref name="hachman">{{Cite news |url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/2099943/microsofts-cortana-digital-assistant-guards-user-privacy-with-notebook.html |title=Microsoft's Cortana digital assistant guards user privacy with 'Notebook' |author=Hachman |first=Mark |date=2014-02-21 |work=PCWorld |accessdate=2014-06-16 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140328084415/http://www.pcworld.com/article/2099943/microsofts-cortana-digital-assistant-guards-user-privacy-with-notebook.html |archive-date=2014-03-28 }}</ref><ref name="verge">{{Cite web |title=This is Cortana, Microsoft's answer to Siri |url=https://www.theverge.com/2014/3/3/5465264/microsoft-cortana-windows-phone-screenshots |accessdate=2014-06-16 |author=Warren |date=2014-03-03 |first=Tom |publisher=The Verge |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141120121804/http://www.theverge.com/2014/3/3/5465264/microsoft-cortana-windows-phone-screenshots |archive-date=2014-11-20 }}</ref>

小娜有一个内置的提醒系统，例如，用户与小娜进行交互并进行相应设定时，它会在用户到达之前设定的特定的提醒时间或地点时，提醒用户与之前设定的联系人通信。<ref>{{Cite web |title=How to set a person-based reminder with Cortana. |url=http://www.windowscentral.com/how-to-person-based-reminder-cortana |author=Guim |date=2014-04-26 |first=Mark |work=Windows Central (Mobile Nations) |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190203144245/https://www.windowscentral.com/how-to-person-based-reminder-cortana |archive-date=2019-02-03 }}</ref>最初这些提醒仅限于安装了小娜的设备，但自Windows 10以来，可以在设备之间进行同步提醒<ref>{{Cite web |title=Windows 10: Cortana now syncs reminders. |url=http://www.neowin.net/news/windows-10-cortana-now-syncs-reminders |author=Sams |date=2015-02-13 |first=Brad |work=Neowin |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716033449/http://www.neowin.net/news/windows-10-cortana-now-syncs-reminders |archive-date=2016-07-16 }}</ref>。

小娜还内置有音乐识别服务<ref name="GroovyPost">{{Cite news |url=http://www.groovypost.com/news/windows-phone-8-1-cortana-identifies-songs/ |title=Use Cortana on Windows Phone 8.1 to Identify Songs |author=Burgess |first=Brian |date=2014-04-19 |work=GroovyPost |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190203024304/https://www.groovypost.com/news/windows-phone-8-1-cortana-identifies-songs/ |archive-date=2019-02-03 }}</ref>。自2014年10月推出[[Microsoft_Lumia#Lumia更新|Lumia Denim手机系列]]以来，小娜增加了“积极倾听”（{{Lang-en|active listening}}）功能，说“你好，小娜”（{{Lang|en|Hey Cortana}}）后即可唤醒小娜，进行操作。<ref name="WindowsCentral">{{Cite news |url=http://www.windowscentral.com/hands-on-hey-cortana-video |title=Hands on with 'Hey Cortana' and the Lumia 930 Denim update |author=Rubino |first=Daniel |date=2015-01-12 |work=Windows Central |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190203150122/https://www.windowscentral.com/hands-on-hey-cortana-video |archive-date=2019-02-03 }}</ref>小娜还整合了[[Foursquare|Foursquare]]等服务，提供餐厅和景点的内容推荐；整合了{{Le|LIFX|LIFX}}，用于控制智能灯泡<ref name="PCWorld">{{Cite news |url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/2458949/windows-phones-cortana-taps-foursquare-to-suggest-nearby-places-of-interest.html |title=Windows Phone's Cortana taps Foursquare to suggest nearby places of interest |author=Newman |first=Jared |date=2014-07-29 |work=PCWorld |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170512140439/http://www.pcworld.com/article/2458949/windows-phones-cortana-taps-foursquare-to-suggest-nearby-places-of-interest.html |archive-date=2017-05-12 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.cnet.com/news/the-new-lifx-windows-10-app-lets-cortana-toggle-your-lights/ |title=The new Lifx Windows 10 app lets Cortana toggle your lights |author=Crist |first=Ry |date=2015-10-15 |publisher=[[CNET|CNET]] |dead-url=no |access-date=2019-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181017001716/https://www.cnet.com/news/the-new-lifx-windows-10-app-lets-cortana-toggle-your-lights/ |archive-date=2018-10-17 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Cortana now taps into Foursquare to give you recommendations for lunch |url=https://www.engadget.com/2014/07/29/cortana-now-taps-into-foursquare-to-give-you-recommendations-for/#prclt-dRLWS1hv |accessdate=2016-10-08 |work=engadget.com |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009173513/https://www.engadget.com/2014/07/29/cortana-now-taps-into-foursquare-to-give-you-recommendations-for/#prclt-dRLWS1hv |archive-date=2016-10-09 }}</ref>。从2016年底开始，小娜集成了微软收购的[[奇妙清單|奇妙清单]]，允许小娜添加和操作提醒。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Hey Cortana... |url=https://www.wunderlist.com/blog/hey-cortana/ |accessdate=2017-05-10 |date=2016-11-17 |work=Wunderlist Blog |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116104649/https://www.wunderlist.com/blog/hey-cortana/ |archivedate=2017-11-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>小娜也可以解决数学[[方程|方程]]，转换计量单位，确定包括[[比特币|比特币]]在内的货币之间的兑换率<ref>{{Cite web |title=Here's how to make the most of Cortana, the Windows 10 digital assistant |url=http://www.digitaltrends.com/computing/get-know-cortana-windows-10/ |accessdate=2015-01-29 |author=Sieber |date=2015-01-28 |first=Tina |publisher=Digital Trends |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150131021722/http://www.digitaltrends.com/computing/get-know-cortana-windows-10/ |archive-date=2015-01-31 }}</ref>，进行长句翻译<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.ithome.com/html/windowsphone/125908.htm |title=Cortana微软小娜多浪漫，7种语言说我爱你 |author=玄隐 |date=2015-01-26 |work=IT之家 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160704012953/http://www.ithome.com/html/windowsphone/125908.htm |archive-date=2016-07-04 |accessdate=2019-02-19 }}</ref>等。<!-- 注释出：[[File:Cortana_WP8.1.png|缩略图]] -->

