-02-19 |accessdate=2019-02-19 }}</ref>；问出“[[士官長_(最後一戰)|士官长]]是谁”时，小娜会使用《[[光环3|光环3]]》的台词“我是他的盾牌，我是他的利刃，我深知他，连同他的过去和未来”回复<ref>{{Cite web |title=Unwrap Cortana's Easter eggs |url=https://www.cnet.com/pictures/cortana-easter-eggs/ |accessdate=2021-12-29 |author=Savvides |date=2015-07-28 |first=Lexy |publisher=CNET |dead-url=no |archive-date=2022-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220418191928/https://www.cnet.com/pictures/cortana-easter-eggs/ }}</ref>。

